T1  - The implications of financial cooperation in Israel's semi-cooperative villages
AU  - Levy, Ammon
AU  - Justman, Moshe
AU  - Hochman, Eithan
JO  - Journal of Development Economics
VL  - 30
IS  - 1
SP  - 25
